reviews.text: food is excellent.  service is good

Came here for Sunday lunch for two. Very good value set lunch for two: soup, fish and chips, paella, pork ribs and choice of drink costing 588 HKD for both of us. Good choice also if you’re collecting Asia Miles (2 HKD = 1 mile on weekends). Loses a star because the staff were a little inexperienced (young). Would come back for casual lunch with a group or a friend.

Simply awesome.
This restaurant ticks out all my rating criteria without a doubt. The staff was friendly and welcoming, which was definitely worth a mention. The design and ambience in general was wonderful, cozy and decoration was the perfect touch to it. It wasn't very crowded, that's a plus. The food was the most memorable part of the dining experience and everything was hot, freshly-cooked, and tasty without a doubt. Prefect for small groups. This restaurant did not disappoint me at all, and I am almost definite that I will come again. 
The fruit tea was awesome. Cheap price for what it promises. Make sure you try it.

Really great and wonderful place to go
The environment is nice and service is good!
I try the new tea set. It's really great and special for summer. 
I loved the blueberry scone with butterfly pea with fresh cream and jam and avocado prawn toast roll! 
The sweet food is nice and good looking. The golden apple crumble is the best for me!

Went for lunch.  Food is pretty good but price a tad bit expensive.  We had the pizza and the pasta from the set menu.  The environment is what gives it 5 stars because the tables are reasonably spaced so you can sit comfortably.  Situated on the 25/F gives it a lot of natural light.  Overall a good place to enjoy your lunch with friends.

result.formatted_address: 25/F, 202 Queen's Rd E, Wan Chai, 香港
result.name: Espuma

reviews.text: 帶子凍而不熟，risotto 無味難吃，有同職員反應，職員就推說會和廚房反應，甜品ok, 只能說剛合格，這個價可以很容易找到比這餐廳更好，咖啡非常難喝，用我自己咖啡機做得一定比好。最氣憤不夠人手，餐廳已經只有20%滿，職員寧願閒聊不理會客人。結果我拿餐牌去找職員落單。更不知所謂的明明有下午茶餐牌，職員只拿正價餐給你。设有下一次，浪費時間，浪费我口感胃部空間。帶子問題你們一直沒有解釋，只是耍耍我，怕我拿賠償吧！我由頭到尾到尾沒有要求啊！只是你們煮得非常難吃，而且煮不熟！
Try. 要試下先!! 試了⋯⋯坐下傾計，環境是可以。食品質素就一般般，相對值錢就比較貴！
环景一般，食物質数不见得好好。西班牙饭(Deluxe Paella Con Marisco )用料质数差，其中兩只蝦肉质发梅。HK398.- 完全不值。另外烤豬手(Roasted Pork Knuckle)比较干身及内裡不夠 juice, 外面尚算皮脆。
